{"tid":1942944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"庚子拳變120周年 百國聯軍","createTime":"2020-03-25T10:59:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-10T14:17:58.000Z","uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62e6b2b6f10843988394a1d301a4cbe1df825cc6","tid":1942944,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T10:59:02.000Z","msg":"支那腦賤粉蛆=義和團<br />\n雜種=慈禧太后<br />\n<br />\n美軍來了 我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b68bd4e41088ae11880552407e0aa52bdc114104","tid":1942944,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"陳雲=洪秀荃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d1b672594abb6e2bf1312119510f81ab0c5cf86","tid":1942944,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:16:06.000Z","msg":"暴亂今昔 - 陶傑<br />\n<br />\n鄰近地區反日暴亂，香港人隔岸觀火，日本菜照吃，日劇照看，北海道和京都照去（如果日本政府不介意的話），倒是看出一點點名堂。<br />\n都說是義和拳基因復發，但是一百年前的拳匪之亂，與今日稍有不同。<br />\n拳匪除了殺洋人，主要殺中國的基督徒。傳教士在中國做慈善，譬如太原的浸信會，在太原辦醫院，贈醫施藥，山西旱災，浸信會傳教士還到英國歐洲捐款，賑助中國飢民。拳匪之亂，是官方挑起的，<span style=\"color: red;\">山東巡撫毓賢，在太原把傳教士、修女，替他們工作的中國人，還有他們年幼的孩子，全部五花大綁，一個挨一個斬首。</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有一個叫法丁（George Farthing）的牧師，七十多歲，鬚髮皆白，質問這位巡撫，為何濫殺無辜。毓賢抽刀，親自把老牧師砍成身首異處</span>，這件事檔案寄存美國俄亥俄大學的圖書館，歷史學者唐德剛驗證記述。<br />\n毓賢回京，滙報慈禧太后，太后親自寫一個「福」字獎賞。有此默許，義和拳自然各地流竄，在民間搜掠，見到十字架、聖經、英文書籍的家戶，不問情由，拖出男女老少，不是砍頭，就是活埋。短短一年不到，全國華裔天主教徒屠殺二萬，基督教徒五千。<br />\n明明是拉登和塔利班的隔代宗師，義和拳是二十世紀第一宗「由國家資助的恐怖主義」（State-sponsored Terrorism），因為中國歷史課本洗腦，歪曲為「愛國運動」，所以今日鄰近地區的人民發癲，日本人不敢殺，這是他們比義和拳膽子小的地方，卻專找開日本汽車的中國人來砸。義和拳殺的是有精神文明信仰的中國人，而今日反日暴徒，燒砸日本車，車主沒什麼信仰，只是簡單的消費者，這一點，不知是鄰近地區的進步還是退步。<br />\n歷史重演，就很好笑了。反日燒日本車，如果德國總理麥克萊接見達賴喇嘛，承認西藏獨立，並支持日本擁尖閣主權，我不明白：憤怒的民眾，豈不是把全國官員書記的黑色平治砸光？那時都改坐紅旗牌？"},{"pid":"93980750e032667eeb4a342171d3ffc1cb935d12","tid":1942944,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-10T14:17:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: teal;\">【國際戰線，靠你支持！】</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\">頂住人民幣，對抗大外宣</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>為美國醫護捐贈醫療物資</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcharity.gofundme.com%2Fo%2Fen%2Fcampaign%2Fmasks-empowerment-campaign&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=d47b8d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://charity.gofundme.com/o/en/campaign/masks-empowerment-campaign</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>美國人權基金會成立「香港專案小組」</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhrf-hk-desk.funraise.org%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=7ebb176d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hrf-hk-desk.funraise.org/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>支援台灣登報，俾世界聽到中國以外既聲音</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.zeczec.com/projects/thisattackcomesfromtaiwan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.zeczec.com%2Fprojects%2Fthisattackcomesfromtaiwan&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=c509dad9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.zeczec.com/projects/thisattackcomesfromtaiwan</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>【登記選民，請即行動！】</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk2020.vote/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk2020.vote%2F&d=D0cCki4bmudO7bhudq%2BynyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=1c992e29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk2020.vote/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces